the $\\alpha$-relaxation of the ergodic\nphase, we find a power-law divergence of the time scale $\\tau_{\\alpha}$ as we\napproach the transition. Through these results, we establish that this new\ntheory is able to reproduce the salient features of MCT, but has the advantages\nof a first principles derivation and a clear mechanism for making systematic\nimprovements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Nov 2014 17:44:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-12"}
