e imparted to a deformable body. Stochastic YORP,\nin particular, will affect the evolution of collisional families whose orbits\ndrift apart under the influence of Yarkovsky forces, in observable ways.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Nov 2014 00:08:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Dec 2014 17:56:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
