al flux cause the different distribution\nbetween GX 17+2 and XTE J1701-462 in the $rms_{\\rm{break}}$-$rms_{\\rm{HBO}}$\ndiagram.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Nov 2014 03:18:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
